HEADWORD: Chalazion
<hw>Cha*la"zi*on</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr.
<?/ dim. of <?/ hail, pimple.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A small
